

Token based authentication
     Client                                             Server
                      -> gửi log-in(1)
   Save JWT(3)       <- gửi encrypted{JWT}(2)
                  -> gửi auth req với JWT header(4)     Xác thực(5)
                     <- gửi response(6)

JWT có 3 phần :
- header : + type
           + thuật toán
- payload : + user
            + init time
- signature : + hash của header + payload + secret salt

Post public : sign up, verify token


<dependency>
			<groupId>com.nimbusds</groupId>
			<artifactId>nimbus-jose-jwt</artifactId>
			<version>9.30.1</version>
		</dependency>
<dependency>
			<groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
			<artifactId>spring-boot-starter-oauth2-resource-server</artifactId>
		</dependency>



